OL,6,FLinda Irvine explained how her son was
OL,7,F"much loved" and a "dependable friend"
OL,8,Fwho "relished his role as a big
OL,9,Fbrother".
OL,11,FShe added: "They say your legacy is
OL,12,Fwhat you leave in people. Frazer will
OL,13,Fnever see his dreams come to fruition.
OL,15,F"He was too big a personality to ever
OL,16,Fbe forgotten. His passing has
OL,17,Fdevastated our family, and he is
OL,18,Fmissed every day.
