OL,3,CFamily speak at inquest of 'beautiful
OL,4,Csoul' who died after care failure
OL,6,F"When Frazer used to phone me, he used
OL,7,Fto end them with, 'Love you mum, more
OL,8,Fthan you ever know'.
OL,10,F"In those last moments (...) I only
OL,11,Fhope he knew how much he was loved."
OL,13,FLe Sauteur and Sutherland were found
OL,14,Fguilty of failing to provide adequate
OL,15,Fcare to Mr Irvine in the moments
OL,16,Fbefore his death under Jersey's Health
OL,17,Fand Safety Law.
