OL,3,CFamily speak at inquest of 'beautiful
OL,4,Csoul' who died after care failure
OL,6,FDuring the trial last June, the Royal
OL,7,FCourt heard how the medics had failed
OL,8,Fto put Mr Irvine in the recovery
OL,9,Fposition, did not recognise he was
OL,10,Fstruggling to breathe, and failed to
OL,11,Fprovide adequate care during
OL,12,Fresuscitation.
OL,14,FThey were sentenced to a two-year
OL,15,Fconditional discharge and ordered to
OL,16,Fpay #500 each in court costs.
OL,18,FTheir subsequent appeal to overturn
OL,19,Fthe conviction failed in October, and
OL,20,Fboth men ultimately resigned from the
OL,21,Fservice at the start of this year.
