OL,6,FAs part of the inquiry, Jersey
OL,7,FAmbulance Service and the States of
OL,8,FJersey Police will be judged on
OL,9,Fwhether there were any shortcomings in
OL,10,Fpolicies, procedures or guidance which
OL,11,Fcould be relevant to Mr Irvine's death
OL,12,Fand if changes may help prevent
OL,13,Fsimilar deaths in the future.
OL,15,FThe inquest is expected to continue
OL,16,Funtil Friday 13 June.
